text: Philip Jeck (15 November 1952 – 25 March 2022Philip Jeck, Experimental Composer and Turntablist, Dies at 69)Staff. "Philip Jeck – CV" . www.philipjeck.com. was an English composer and multimedia artist. He was best known for his use of looping devices and both analogue and digital effects. He worked for Touch Records. ==References== Category:1952 births Category:2022 deaths Category:English composers Category:English musicians
